com.cisco.pxgrid.stub.identity

Interface SessionDirectoryQuery


  • public interface SessionDirectoryQuery
    An interface with methods related to querying a session directory for information. Clients typically receive an instance by invoking a static method such as com.cisco.xgrid.identity.client.SessionDirectoryFactory#createQuery(com.cisco.xgrid.gcl.GridConnection, SessionDirectoryProperties).
